> Order (Lâ†’R) indicates the physical sequence of rectifiers from left to right.
U-Position represents the mounting height (Above/Below or specific U-height).

PDSC Number and Frame Number are Verizon-specific custom fields used for internal referencing of power system frames and rectifier groups. These fields are not mandatory for DC-Track import. If the values are available from site documentation, they may be filled; otherwise, they can be left blank.




